query:
SELECT GREATEST(
                       (
                           SELECT MAX(number)
                           FROM miniblocks
                           WHERE eth_precommit_tx_id IS NOT NULL
                       ),
                       (
                           SELECT MAX(number)
                           FROM miniblocks
                           WHERE l1_batch_number =
                            (
                                 SELECT number
                                 FROM l1_batches
                                          JOIN eth_txs ON l1_batches.eth_commit_tx_id = eth_txs.id
                                 WHERE eth_txs.confirmed_eth_tx_history_id IS NOT NULL
                                 ORDER BY number DESC
                                 LIMIT 1
                            )
                       ),
                        0
                    ) AS number
